Corrosion Under Insulation.
The software helps to get as well as plot the raw data from VNA device configured with the software. To acheive the same, user is required to provide the config file(using configuration panel mentioned below) and then provide configuration paramter.Upon completion of the afore mentioned task, the software fetches the data and plots the same on the screen shown.
Functionalities on this form:
Configration: This button navigates you to the configuration panel, where in you can provide the configuration file and configuration paramters. for more details click on the configuration button and and then help.
Start DAQ: This button navigates you to the plotting panel, showing plot of data fetched against previous set configuration. If the configuration is not done earlier or is reset, then the user can only use this feature after completing the same.
Reset: The software will clear all previous set configuration(including the configuration paramters,configuration file) Upon this action, user in case wish to use start DAQ feature will be required to complete the configuration process through configuration panel
